357
00:38:51,510 --> 00:38:54,250
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Benar, itu karena dia semakin sombong.</i></font>

358
00:38:54,380 --> 00:38:58,520
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Apa kau melihat wajahnya
saat dimarahi bos?</i></font>

359
00:38:58,610 --> 00:39:04,760
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Pak. Senior Saiki
dijebak oleh senior lain.</i></font>

360
00:39:04,890 --> 00:39:09,730
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Itu karena posisi Senior Saiki
