361
00:39:09,890 --> 00:39:12,390
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Terima kasih atas laporannya.</i></font>

362
00:39:23,240 --> 00:39:25,650
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Senior Saiki!</i></font>

363
00:39:30,410 --> 00:39:35,720
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kenapa kau diam saja?
